Package commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddDoctorCommand
    Command to add a doctor into the system.
    AddPatientCommand
    Command to add a patient into the system.
    AssignBedCommand
    Command to assign a patient to a specific bed in the ward.
    AssignDoctorCommand
    Command to assign a doctor to a patient.
    CommandStatus
    The common ancestor for all commands that records whether the last execution of the command was successful, and if not, records the error message.
    CreateWardCommand
    The command to create and initialize the one instance of Ward.
    CurrentStateCommand
    Command to obtain a String representation of the current state of the system.
    DropAssocCommand
    Command to drop the association between a doctor and a patient.
    EmptyBedsCommand
    Command to obtain the list of empty beds for the ward The list is accessible via the method getEmptyBedsList.
    ReleasePatientCommand
    Command to release a patient from his/her bed in the ward.
